{"tid":2307363,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"呢條片1945 lost girl係咩料","createTime":"2020-12-01T06:35:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-01T06:56:02.000Z","uid":282619,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f273e3a6b3662fcaba5da44960f28621fed5ba3f","tid":2307363,"uid":282619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T06:35:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/dQWv9KpDWEg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FdQWv9KpDWEg&d=3wrM%2FJom4zLweqSprMIx0mINpH3PnqyTY83oYMeb7B8%3D&h=204b1169\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/dQWv9KpDWEg</a><br />\n有人話係1945年蘇聯紅軍性暴力下其中一個受害人<br />\n但1945唔係打完啦咩，仲有慰安婦？同埋呢啲無軍事法庭審？<br />\n我以為得亞洲有慰安婦，原來歐洲都有慰安婦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48e2d989f421cd454ad2f5cf000c755529e47067","tid":2307363,"uid":224561,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T06:56:02.000Z","msg":"1945 5月先係打完歐洲戰場<br />\n而蘇聯紅軍由進入德國開始，一直都有強姦德國女人<br />\n蘇聯紅軍高層亦唔想阻止/阻止唔到<br />\n佢地同慰安婦唔同，慰安婦係有規劃性<br />\n德國呢啲係單純強姦<br />\n受害女性點數量過百萬<br />\n<br />\n至於點解戰後冇事<br />\n因為蘇聯係勝利一方<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}